criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Office computer workers who worked for a minimum of four hours per day using a
             computer

          -  With or without neck/shoulder pian

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Involved regular strength training of the neck/upper extremities within the past 12
             months;

          -  history of whiplash, neck/upper limb fractures, previous surgery and previous clinical
             treatment for a neck/upper limb injury within the last 12 months;

          -  Fibromyalgia;

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  Neurological disorders.
